name: Liquid Sound Studios old school demo
description: “Liquid Sound Studios old school demo” encompasses some of the best of three years of recording, experimenting with different sounds and recording techniques. Most of the songs were created at the time of recording. All of the tracks were recorded at Liquid Sound Studios with the exception of “Airplane Blues” which was recorded by Jai Lewis at Subliminal Freedom Studio. All instruments were played/arranged by Zak D. Wass with the exception of the bassline in “Funky Rock 2”, which was played by Jesse Anderson.
